<h1 style="color: #e8e8e8;">New Message on Offer</h1>

<p style="color: #b7b7b7;">Hello {{userDisplayName}},</p>

<p style="color: #b7b7b7;">A new message has been sent on your offer:</p>

<div
  style="background-color: rgba(45, 55, 72, 0.5); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid rgb(45, 55, 72);"
>
  <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #e8e8e8;">Offer #{{offer.id}}</h2>
  <div
    style="margin-top: 15px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(45, 55, 72);"
  >
    <p style="color: #b7b7b7; margin: 0;"><strong>{{message.author}}</strong>
      sent a message:</p>
    <p style="color: #b7b7b7; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">{{message.content}}</p>
  </div>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="button">View Offer</a>
</p>